약침, 한약, 보약, 공진단, 경옥고 - 원장 소개 * 문학진 원장 - 경희대학교 한의학 박사 - 경희대학교 외래교수 - 전) 청구경희한의원 원장 - 전) 경희대학교 겸임교수 - 척추 신경추나의학회 회원 - 대한응용근신...</p>\n                                        <p class=\"se-oglink-url\">booking.naver.com</p>\n                                    </div>\n                                </a>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module='{\"type\":\"v2_oglink\", \"id\" :\"SE-3858986d-3df6-45e6-943e-3a5118e76547\", \"data\" : {\"link\" : \"https://booking.naver.com/booking/13/bizes/331349\", \"isVideo\" : \"false\", \"thumbnail\" : \"https://dthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/?src&#x3D;%22https%3A%2F%2Fldb-phinf.pstatic.net%2F20221126_244%2F1669435214967kEbru_PNG%2F%25C0%25CC%25BC%25F6_%25BD%25BA%25B8%25B6%25C6%25AE%25C7%25C3%25B7%25B9%25C0%25CC%25BD%25BA_%25B8%25DE%25C0%25CE_copy.png%3Ftype%3Df804_408_60_sharpen%22&amp;type&#x3D;ff500_300\"}}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2ac44de9-a89a-4e66-b5c7-997aabfa0966\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-1ff9b8f7-ddea-4dff-9bf4-8e2bd0242cd9\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-73332065-5746-4b0a-a0f5-42437beb770e\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>    </div>",
